    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos(v1))
    v1 = (0.77 - (wp.abs(v0 + 0.86) + (tmp + 0.66 + v1 + 0.18)))

    v1 = ((0.56 + tmp) + v1)
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.60)) + (wp.cos(v2 + 0.83) * 0.91))
    data[tid] = v0
